 Reverse Geocode # Endpoint Info # method: POST path: /api/v1/reverse-geocode/ body: GeoJSON Point Geometry Notes # Reverse geocode endpoint returns lowest available GADM level contains a given point as a GeoJSON Feature
Request body must include valid GeoJSON Point Geometry
Example # curl -X POST -H &#34;Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN&#34;\ -H &#34;Content-Type: application/json&#34; \ -d &#39;{&#34;type&#34;: &#34;Point&#34;, &#34;coordinates&#34;: [ -0.017369731082479873, 44.12916742279152]}&#39; \ &#34;https://api.gadm-api.org/api/v1/reverse-geocode/&#34;
